# Ignore service account keys
backend/app/keys/service-account.json
backend/app/keys/*.json


---

## 📂 `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.env

# Node
node_modules/
build/
dist/

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Docker
*.dockerfile
*.tar

# Terraform
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl
*.auto.tfvars

# Secrets
*.json
*.key
*.pem
.env
